2054.subject: HPWE
2054.descrlong: Focuses on the theoretical and practical aspects of backcountry leadership. Topics include leadership styles, group facilitation, risk management, and minimum impact camping techniques. Requires a weeklong intensive backpacking expedition to the Sierra Nevada Mountains. Course fee required. (Offered fall semester.)
